    Interface Description
    AssembledWigetDef

    ContainerDef
    An abstract defintion of a container as required to generate the template assembly java source code
    FamilyDef
    An abstract defintion of a wiget family as required to generate the template assembly java source code
    FieldDef

    MethodDef
    An abstract defintion of a java method as required to generate the template assembly java source code
    TemplateDef

    TypeDef

    WigetContainerBindingDef

    WigetParameterBindingDef<V>
    The defintion of a wiget parameter binding
